data.description:
***Price Improvement***
Welcome to this delightful 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom plus game room home. Upon entering you will be greeted by the abundance of natural light making the home feel bright and inviting and the open floor plan creates a spacious and flowing layout. The beautiful laminate flooring is an upgrade and is not only aesthetically pleasing but also easy to maintain. In the kitchen you have upgraded cabinets and counter tops all stainless steel appliances. Make your way upstairs where you will find the game room, master suite and master bathroom. The upgrades in the master bath include tile around the separate shower, tub and double vanity adding a nice touch. Secondary bedrooms and full-size bathroom offer plenty of room for family members or guests. Large, fully fenced backyard is a great feature for privacy and security. It's perfect for families with children or pets, offering a safe and spacious area to play and enjoy outdoor activities.
